  <summary date="2021-01-11T19:14:07Z" status="Introduced in House">Reducing Obesity in Youth Act of 2020

This bill requires the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, in coordination with the Administration for Children and Families, to award grants to nonprofits, institutions of higher education, or consortia of these entities to promote healthy eating and physical activity among children in early care and education settings.</summary>
